{"tid":1536200,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣安慰失戀既朋友？","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:30:13.000Z","uid":61100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"024896ff729151a1ababe440fdfa1327b0b339b2","tid":1536200,"uid":61100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:02:01.000Z","msg":"朋友失戀大半年 但仲未走出黎 仲有自殺傾向<br />\n晚晚不停喊 喊到崩潰哂 個人完全冇動力做任何野 <br />\n想約佢出黎食飯傾訴下又唔肯 只係靠msg 電話知道佢近況  我要講既野 道理都講野  但佢就係好似活係自己世界  佢已經講過好多次要跳樓 好驚佢有一日真係做....  我可以做啲咩去幫佢 好擔心佢 好驚佢做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n可以失望 不要絕望<br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"f7e28a82421b16561132d2d0ce10c85592a13b7f","tid":1536200,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:03:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50409031b82624a63010cbd6c822985bb3c62e43","tid":1536200,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Renq43y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRenq43y.jpg&h=bb73b46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2FTuve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2FTuve.jpg&h=3a22dffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbetioz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxbetioz.jpg&h=8f95a040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1513398/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1513398/page/1</a><br />\n如何不仇警？"},{"pid":"4761aa9cb66011162718b88c87928c45efb49b3b","tid":1536200,"uid":311122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"失戀走唔出<br />\n日日諗返以前啲嘢<br />\n諗好多對過去每一個決定嘅假設<br />\n其實過咗去都冇得追究<br />\n試下介紹新對象俾佢分散下注意力？"},{"pid":"0f44f53cefcea9208cbbe5cbea4c1f7b353a1317","tid":1536200,"uid":240812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:21:48.000Z","msg":"不需要安慰 道理都明白陪伴就很好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23579d5defdd1abce121502e1c1df0215cb729f3","tid":1536200,"uid":61100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4761aa9cb66011162718b88c87928c45efb49b3b","tid":1536200,"uid":311122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"失戀走唔出<br />\n日日諗返以前啲嘢<br />\n諗好多對過去每一個決定嘅假設<br />\n其實過咗去都冇得追究<br />\n試下介紹新對象俾佢分散下注意力？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:44